msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Oh, that laughter's coming from the bar..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Come to think of it, I haven't gone\r\ninto a bar for laughs and drinks here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Well, I guess I drank with Haruto at\r\nKiyomi's bar... But he was drinking milk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Hm? What're ya doin' standing out\r\nhere gawkin' at the bar?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Oh, I get it, y'must be too nervous\r\nto go in because it's your first time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "N-No, that's not it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "No need t'feel ashamed,\r\nI was in your shoes once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "I remember peekin' in the door a bit\r\nt'see what it was like inside..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Yer lookin' like a newcomer to\r\nbar culture. That right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "I don't know if that's really a thing,\r\nbut yeah, I grew out of the bar scene."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Alrighty then! Fate musta sent ya\r\nmy way, then. I'll join ya. C'mon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "W-Wait, I never said I wanted to..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Now now, not another word. It's my treat. \r\n'Sides, a drink with Mama cures what ails ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Not t'mention drinking buddies.\r\nStep on in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Heh... Well, one glass wouldn't hurt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "That's the spirit! C'mon now!\r\nNo time like the present."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Hey Mama, I'm back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Welcome back, Hatakeyama-san!\r\nThis a friend of yours?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "He was peepin' inside, so I invited him in.\r\nUm... Oh wait, I didn't catch yer name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Oh, I'm Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, eh?\r\nI'm Hatakeyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Glad t'meetchya, Kiryu-san.\r\nWelcome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Tch, y'ain't welcome. I don't much\r\ncare fer strangers gettin' in my space."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Hey Kaneko-san. Don't be like that.\r\nThe bar's open to everyone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Feh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "W-Well, we have some fussy regulars, but\r\nhe'll warm up t'ya the more ya stop in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "That all it takes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Let's just have a drink. I'll show ya\r\nhow t'enjoy yourself at a bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Oh, Mama, gimme the usual.\r\nMake it double for Kiryu-san here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Alrighty then, lemme give ya the\r\nscoop on small town bar culture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Hey, don't get too big fer yer\r\nbritches now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "I-I know that!\r\nI'm doin' him a kindness here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "'Sides, if Kiryu-san becomes a regular,\r\nit's your sales goin' up, ain't it Mama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "That's a fine point. Hatakeyama-san,\r\nyou tell him jus' how great we are, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Anyhow, bars are great for enjoying a drink\r\nand a chat with all sortsa different folks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Sometimes we even gather around\r\nto have a long, lively conversation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Huh, everyone's like family then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Those talks are a right good time. Though\r\nwe usually talk about pretty dumb stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Mhm, Kiryu-san, once you're friendly with\r\neveryone, join in and liven up conversations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "O-Okay, got it.\r\nI need to be friendly, huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Oh, y'ain't worried about all this, are ya?\r\nDon't be, everyone here's good at heart."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Exactly, don't sweat it. All the\r\nregulars here have their particulars."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Right, Kaneko-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Oh, shut it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Some day soon you'll fit right in\r\nwith us here, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "My bar offers karaoke n' darts, too.\r\nNothin' beats those fer makin' friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah, Gen-san loves his karaoke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Doesn't he?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Heh, seems like a lively little place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Yeah, 'cept most of us're all old men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "So all these older guys have their\r\neyes on the mama then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Well, sure Mama's a pretty number,\r\nbut she don't put up with no tomfoolery."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Oh, y'see that sofa yonder?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "The center seat is the throne of the\r\nbar... A man has t'earn that seat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Th-Throne...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Unless you're the king of regulars,\r\ny'ain't allowed t'drink from that spot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "In other words, it means it's reserved\r\nfor the one true King of New Gaudi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "King of New Gaudi... Huh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "And, y'best known Mama's approval don't\r\ncome easy. She's a tough cookie to figure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "She's genuine and nice, but a right mystery.\r\nShe don't jus' open her heart to anyone..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Hatakeyama-san, I can hear every word!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Oh no, that's um, not my opinion.\r\nJus' word 'round the campfire..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "So much fer my chance at the throne..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "W-Well, Kiryu-san, if y'want to sit there,\r\ny'best start gettin' friendly with folks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Hmm, I see. Basically, I just need\r\nto talk to all the customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "That's right. If y'keep widening your\r\ncircle, only good'll come of it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Like I said, all the regulars here are good folks.\r\nThey're there when you need them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Heh... Is that so? Thanks for today.\r\nI had a great time and a nice drink."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Let's drink again soon, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "We'll be here fer ya, Kiryu-san.\r\nAnd Hatakeyama-san, let's have some words."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "The New Gaudi Bar, huh? Might be a nice\r\nplace to come in for a drink once in a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "There's some real characters here.\r\nMaybe I'll even make some friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "I'll check back if I find the time."
msgstr ""

